item.title: ZW32-24-outdoor-high-voltage-vacuum-circuit-breaker
item.description: ZW32-24/630-25 outdoor high-voltage AC vacuum circuit breaker is an outdoor power distribution equipment with a rated voltage of 24kV and three-phase AC 50Hz. It is a switchgear developed by our company according to the long-term planning of my country's power system and relevant standards. It has the ability to break and close the load current, overload current and short-circuit current in the line.
